{
  "name": "Id Insinuation",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You unleash a torrent of conflicting desires in the mind of one creature you can see within range, impairing its ability to make decisions. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be incapacitated. At the end of each of its turns, it takes [[/r 1d12]] psychic damage, and it can then make another Wisdom saving throw. On a success, the spell ends on the target.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
